lead_paragraph: New York's highest state court has ruled that a lawsuit by the Algosaibi family conglomerate, claiming that a Saudi billionaire who married into the family committed a $150 million fraud, should be heard in Saudi Arabia.

headline.main: N.Y. Court Dismisses Claims Over Saudi Billionaire's Alleged Fraud
headline.print_headline: N.Y. Court Dismisses Claims Over Saudi Billionaire's Alleged Fraud
